      <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
	<p>
	  (No translation offered by Senart; “it is clear
	  that the inscription commemorated the donation of
	  a cistern, made, it seems, by nuns, and that the
	  date referred to the winter of the 5th year of
	  some sovereign.”)
	</p>
